<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink57-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">talaimakaṟkup puṟattoḻukkam uḷatāyiṟṟu eṉpatu kēṭṭa tōḻi avaṉai viṉāyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink57">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>pakaliṟ ṟōṉṟum palkatirt tīyi</l>
<l>ṉāmpalañ ceṟuviṟ ṟēṉū raṉṉa</l>
<l>vivaṇalam pulampap piriya</l>
<l>vaṉainala muṭaiyaḷō makiḻnaniṉ peṇṭē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


  
  
<l>   Is your [new] girlfriend really a woman of such beauty, o delightful man, </l> 
<l>   that you'd leave lonely the beauty of this girl  </l> 
<l>   who is like Tēṉūr </l> 
<l rend="indent2">   with its white-lotus fields </l> 
<l rend="indent2">   like many-rayed fires </l> 
<l rend="indent2">   that shine bright as day? </l> 
  
    
    
    </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
